data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the exclusive gated community of Fairway Oaks, Mulberry FL! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts an additional office/den, offering the perfect blend of comfort and functionality.    Step inside and be greeted by a spacious and bright living area, adorned with large windows that allow natural light to cascade throughout. The heart of the home is a well-appointed kitchen featuring modern appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar – perfect for entertaining guests or preparing family meals.    The master suite provides a tranquil retreat, complete with an ensuite bathroom for added privacy and an oversized walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms ensure there's plenty of space for family, guests, or a home office. The versatile office/den adds a valuable extra space for work or relaxation, catering to your individual needs.    Noteworthy features include a brand-new roof installed in February 2023, offering peace of mind and long-lasting durability. The exterior of the home was tastefully painted in 2021, enhancing curb appeal and ensuring a fresh, modern look.  Commercial grade vinyl plank flooring was installed in June of 2023 in the living areas.     One of the highlights of this property is the fully fenced-in yard, providing a secure and private oasis for outdoor activities with a 30amp generator hookup. The yard includes a 2022 shed, offering additional storage space for tools, equipment, or recreational gear. Enjoy the luxury of no rear neighbors, providing a serene backdrop for your daily life.    Fairway Oaks, with its gated entry, offers a sense of security and exclusivity. The community is known for its well-maintained surroundings and friendly atmosphere. Conveniently located in Mulberry, you'll have easy access to local amenities, schools, and parks, making it an ideal setting for a family home.  This home qualifies for 100% financing through USDA financing!
